title: Cowboys, Rams, Super Bowl teams, and Baker Mayfield
itunes:title: Cowboys, Rams, Super Bowl teams, and Baker Mayfield
description:
Colin discusses the uncertainty of Dallas Cowboys HC Jason Garrett, why the Los Angeles Rams traded for Jalen Ramsey, the 8 teams he believes can win the Super Bowl, and his thoughts on Cleveland Browns QB Baker Mayfield's decision making. Guests include Doug Gottlieb, Joel Klatt, Steve Palazzolo, and Bucky Brooks,
